About Colosseum Eternal

Colosseum runs two hackathons per year, each followed by a new Sponsors cohort of winners. Eternal is your opportunity throughout the year to compete for the recurring Eternal Award, as well as admittance into Solana's leading Sponsors program.

The Eternal Award celebrating Solana's most innovative products

All builders who successfully submit will be eligible to win the Eternal Award, which will be presented semi-annually to the team whose product innovation drives the entire Solana ecosystem forward.

Judged by top Solana ecosystem founders

Eternal product submissions will be evaluated by the Colosseum team, leading ecosystem founders, and former hackathon winners.

Build, scale & succeed with Colosseum's Sponsors

8 week hybrid online + IRL program

Elite founder network

250K in pre-seed funding

1:1 mentorship

Exclusive founder resources
